%85%E6%8C%81%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=9ca1c4d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2394711/【反修例】市民為絕食人士送暖%E3%80%8073歲陳伯絕逾140小時血壓低：會堅持到最後</a> 幾個鐘前新聞"},{"pid":"70d31c8c7f0fe9cd9faab941e6bb3de7c0aded4b","tid":1296130,"uid":267527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"8/7 1400<br />\n頭先去海富探陳伯<br />\n佢話朝早有醫護人員檢查過 一切正常<br />\n自己亦冇唔舒服 只係喉嚨痛<br />\n我見佢都健康算精神 傾計好正常。<br />\n佢話希望大家可以帶個信息<br />\n佢已經對政府絕望<br />\n佢咁做係想同年青人講 唔好輕生<br />\n要珍惜生命<br />\n一定可以用其他方法去解決問題。<br />\n而佢亦話會答應大家 唔會俾自己出事<br />\n不過暫時仲想頂多陣。<br />\n佢目前有兩宗司法覆核搞緊<br />\n其中一單係DQ<br />\n另一樣因為有其他人探佢就未傾到。<br />\n<br />\n希望有時間又喺附近嘅人<br />\n可以去支持佢 同佢加油打氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEksjqr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEksjqr.png&h=0df673d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56a8ff0c1ab0208ecb74371f5b3f7b5a1bdef758","tid":1296130,"uid":267527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3931c56836990a7f6efba03ade0253d24ac0942","tid":1296130,"uid":249991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:16:26.000Z","msg":"係咪仲絕食緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:16:22.000Z","msg":"是的"},{"pid":"68cce3718db112a2a0045d7231a715046887c134","tid":1296130,"uid":222646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56a8ff0c1ab0208ecb74371f5b3f7b5a1bdef758","tid":1296130,"uid":267527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3931c56836990a7f6efba03ade0253d24ac0942","tid":1296130,"uid":249991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:16:26.000Z","msg":"係咪仲絕食緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:16:22.000Z","msg":"是的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:21:39.000Z","msg":"巴打知唔知而家咩環境，有一班巴絲想去現場勸下陳伯"},{"pid":"796d9ed70b7fa581448d28f7fc51dc7f802f1d00","tid":1296130,"uid":267527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:49:44.000Z","msg":"10/7 1345<br />\n去咗海富探陳伯<br />\n佢仲好精神 <br />\n佢托我同大家報平安<br />\n佢話知道好多人擔心佢<br />\n但目前仲撐到<br />\n到唔妥一定會停止<br />\n叫大家無需太擔心。<br />\n另外佢話今晚7點半有記者會<br />\n希望大家到場支持。"}]}